com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.setup

类 AylaSetupDevice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaDevice
      • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.setup.AylaSetupDevice

  • public class AylaSetupDevice
extends AylaDevice
    Represents an AylaDevice that is used by AylaSetup. This device should only be used during the WiFi setup process and is not considered part of the user's set of devices.
